summary:
**Summary of ASX Announcement (Operational Update - Game Launches & Pipeline)**  

- **Super Flappy Golf (First-Party Title):**  
  - 73,000+ organic installs in first two weeks post-global launch (5 June 2025).  
  - Strong retention rates (~46% Day 1, ~25% Day 7, 10% Day 28).  
  - Monetization: Free-to-play with in-app purchases (AUD $1.99–$19.99) and ad-free upgrade (AUD $5.99).  

- **Ultimate Chicken Horse (Third-Party Title):**  
  - 65,000+ pre-registrations; global mobile launch on 19 June 2025.  
  - "Try-Before-You-Buy" model with one-time unlock (AUD $14.99, 20% discount for two weeks).  

- **Winter Burrow (Third-Party Title):**  
  - 90,000+ Steam wishlists; confirmed for Steam, Xbox (Day 1 on Game Pass), and Nintendo Switch.  
  - Showcased at Summer Games Fest and Wholesome Direct 2025 (100,000+ livestream views).  

- **Other Highlights:**  
  - Two titles (*Death Road to Canada*, *Possessions*) ranked #1 and #2 on Google Play Pass Top Charts (11 June 2025).  
  - Pipeline: *Flick Shot Rogues* (Q3 2025) with 16,000+ Steam wishlists.  

**No material capital/financial data disclosed.**
